room_title: Escape room "Murder on Broadway Street" by Lubbock Escapes in Lubbock
room_description: Dateline 1925. It's the height of Prohibition in Lubbock, Texas. Local accountant Tommy "The Loose End" Malloy has been murdered. Unknown to most, Malloy also ran an illegal speakeasy bar for his criminal-type clients on Broadway Street. Malloy's wife has hired you to investigate her husband's death and, hopefully, to discover the location of his fortune. Unfortunately for you, Malloy's ledgers are missing and his clients are preparing to burn down the speakeasy to keep their secrets safe.
